<div class='listy_headline'>
<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/07/25/sports/football/nfl-cte.html">110 N.F.L. Brains </a>
</div>
<div class='listy_body'>
<p>A neuropathologist examined the brains of 111 N.F.L. player &mdash; <strong>and 110 were found to have C.T.E.,</strong> the degenerative disease linked to repeated blows to the head. <br></p> <blockquote class="listy_blockquote">“It is no longer debatable whether or not there is a problem in football &mdash; there is a problem.” &mdash; <strong>Dr. Ann McKee</strong></blockquote>
</div>
</li>
