<div class='listy_headline'>
<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/2017/08/30/sports/espn-ed-cunningham-football-concussions.html?mtrref=www.google.com">ESPN Football Analyst Walks Away, Disturbed by Brain Trauma on Field</a>
</div>
<div class='listy_body'>
<p>After nearly 20 years of serving as a color analyst for college football games on ESPN and ABC, Ed Cunningham walked away because <strong>he no longer felt comfortable profiting from a sport</strong> he knows is killing its participants.&nbsp;</p> <blockquote class="listy_blockquote">“I take full ownership of my alignment with the sport. I can just no longer be in that cheerleader’s spot.” &mdash; <strong>Ed Cunningham</strong></blockquote>
</div>
</li>
<li class='row list_item clearfix advert_item' id='id-5a40197808720a00012e8127'>
<div class='list-ad-container'>
<div class='ad module articlebig mid1 ad-dfp dfp-size-300x250' data-mobile='TopAd1' id='TopAd1'></div>
</div>
</li>
