<div class='listy_headline'>
<a href="https://www.nytimes.com/interactive/2017/01/09/sports/football/what-happened-within-this-players-skull-football-concussions.html?mtrref=www.google.com">What Happened Within This Player’s Skull</a>
</div>
<div class='listy_body'>
<p>When a college receiver sustained a concussion while wearing a high-tech mouthguard with motion sensors, it gave researchers a detailed window into <strong>what happens to the brain in the milliseconds after a big hit</strong>. This video illustrates the new findings about how the brain is affected by such blows.&nbsp;</p> <blockquote class="listy_blockquote">Think Jell-O, not an egg. You know what happens when you take a plate of Jell-O and give it a hard shake? The stretches and contortions approximate what is happening to all the wiring throughout the brain.</blockquote>
</div>
</li>
<li class='row list_item clearfix ' id='id-5a40247b9db7d8000124d619'>
<figure class='media photo media-viewer-disabled-false horizontal' data-media-action='modal'>
<span class='visually-hidden'>
Photo
</span>
<div class='image'>
<img alt='' class='media-viewer-candidate' data-mediaviewer-caption='Don Horton during a North Carolina State game in 2009.' data-mediaviewer-credit='Ethan Hyman/The News & Observer, via Associated Press' data-mediaviewer-src='https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-jumbo.jpg' data-pattern='{{size}}' data-ratio='0.7373046875' data-widths='[{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-master1050.jpg","size":1050},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-master180.jpg","size":180},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-blog225.jpg","size":225},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-tmagSF.jpg","size":362},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-blog427.jpg","size":427},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-blog480.jpg","size":480},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-master495.jpg","size":495},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-blog533.jpg","size":533},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-tmagArticle.jpg","size":592},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-articleLarge.jpg","size":600},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-master675.jpg","size":675},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-jumbo.jpg","size":1024},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-popup.jpg","size":650},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-slide.jpg","size":600},{"slug":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2017/05/18/sports/00horton3/00horton3-superJumbo.jpg","size":2048},{"slug":null,"size":null}]' src='https://static01.nyt.com/packages/flash/multimedia/ICONS/transparent.png'>
